0.2.name: wordpress/native
0.2.description: This is a starter/base theme for developers designed with HTML5, CSS3. It supports menu descriptions, four widget areas, and much more... Use it as a clean base for your projects. Support at Designed By team. Watch the demo. Requires WordPress 3.1 or higher.
